fields.name: unknown
fields.title: Unknown
fields.description: The cause of this failure is unknown. System administrators should investigate this failure to determine the root cause and make sure it is correctly tracked in the future.

fields.name: database
fields.title: Database
fields.description: An error occurred with the Scale database. System administrators should investigate this failure to determine the root cause and correct it.

fields.name: database-operation
fields.title: Database Operation
fields.description: A Scale database operation failure occurred. This can be caused by issues such as the database reaching its connection limit, being unreachable, query deadlocks, and other operation issues.

fields.name: filesystem-io
fields.title: Filesystem IO
fields.description: An IO operation on the node's local filesystem failed.

fields.name: nfs
fields.title: NFS
fields.description: An NFS (Network File System) operation failed.
